        Upper Leewood Farm Yard<br>
        Effingham Common Road<br>
        Leatherhead<br>
        Surrey, KT24 5JQ<br>
        United Kingdom<br>
        <br>
        Website: <a href="https://surreycontracting.co.uk">https://surreycontracting.co.uk</a><br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@surreycontractinggroup.co.uk">info@surreycontractinggroup.co.uk</a><br>
        Telephone: <a href="tel:01932932650">01932 932650</a>
      </address>

      <p class="policy-meta">Last updated: 1 June 2026.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

